# Database
# The .bak patterns matter: *.db alone does not match names like
# schedule.db.bak-pre290, which is how full database dumps (names, password
# hashes, wages) previously ended up tracked in the repo.
*.db
*.db.*
*.sqlite3
*.bak
*.bak-*
*shm
*wal

